[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    403[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    404[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106m1[38;2;191;97;106m.[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mCase-detail store with explicit access-control discipline.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The case-detail store (line lists with patient identifiers) is a separate AWS account or at minimum a separate VPC subnet with its own KMS key, IAM scoping, CloudTrail data events, and just-in-time access provisioning. Investigators who need to view case detail authenticate with a separate role assumption that requires explicit purpose-of-access documentation; the access is logged for after-the-fact audit.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    405[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
